            "title": "Meta簽署一系列核電協議 為人工智能數據中心供電",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Meta簽署一系列核電協議 為人工智能數據中心供電\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"539\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IirKBQPT6H8hykofF4SDDQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/45a1d600-ee25-11f0-b77f-7b940c38ce25\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Meta簽署一系列核電協議 為人工智能數據中心供電</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
