        {
            "title": "歐洲央行Lane：特朗普政策將使美元受到質疑 歐元料從中受益",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"歐洲央行Lane：特朗普政策將使美元受到質疑 歐元料從中受益\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aY7KAFgblFTYnL_4N3YCAQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/db79e690-e86a-11ed-bfb8-14c52b3bcdb4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">歐洲央行Lane：特朗普政策將使美元受到質疑 歐元料從中受益</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
